    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a medium-sized pot with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> diced onion </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>remaining curry powder </strong>with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min further or until fragrant</p>",
