      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong>,<strong> </strong>then bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 4-5 min or until the sauce has reduced to a thick curry-like consistency</p><p>Once thickened, add the sauce to a <strong>food processor</strong> and blitz until smooth – this is your<strong> curry sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
