    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the<strong> brioche halves</strong> to a baking tray (or two!), cut side up, and put the tray[s] in the oven for 4-5 min or until warmed through</p>",
