    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger, add the <strong>battered basa </strong>to each <strong>toasted brioche base</strong>, then spoon over some of the <strong>curry sauce </strong>and top with a few of the <strong>chips</strong> and a <strong>toasted brioche bun lid </strong>– this is your <strong>chip shop fish & chip burger</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chip shop fish & chip burger </strong>with the<strong> remaining chips</strong>,<strong> dressed salad </strong>and any <strong>remaining curry sauce</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the chips with the<strong> remaining cider vinegar </strong>and enjoy!</p>",
